defaultThis research uses a new analysis
default considering the science workforce across the entire economy, rather than looking at total employees within science based industries. This innovative approach enables an understanding of the true size and scope of the science workforce across the economy, 
defaultrather than limiting the research to considering scientists working in a narrow band of science sectors.
